{
  "stem": "10358.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the Russians, they didn't-- Russians didn't want to give up the town, Ostrog.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I witnessed from my window street fights.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I saw Russian soldiers-- soldiers and German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were fighting with bayonets, And then when the-- when the Russians-- when the Germans left, the Russian soldiers were dying in front of our-- my house.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they were wounded and they were crying in Russian, [RUSSIAN].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That means water.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And-- and I tried to get out and give them water.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "At this point, I heard shots again, and I went in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then he died practically-- from my window I saw him die in front of my eyes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This-- this moment I'll never forget.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'll try to remember now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was about 16 years, two years, right, 16.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we-- and then the Russians defeated and then the Germans took over our town.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were already under the Russian-- under the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans, and then it started, the-- you want me to tell you what the Germans did at that point?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was-- they formed the Jewish committee.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And through this Jewish committee, they gave out orders, the-- to the Jewish people to deliver all the gold and silver, leather to the German city government, which we did.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after that, all the Jews were forced to wear yellow patches.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we all had to wear a yellow patch in front and on the back for identity, the Jewish identity.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And after a month later started the first execution, first [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You-- you-- slowly they prepared us for everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You were just in a shock, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You just don't think.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't think.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't remember thinking.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
